    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I don't think that is possible, and I also don't think we _want_ to support that (it is more logical that you want different columns in different colors, and that is what is done by providing a list. I don't see a way to do both with a clean API)\n\nBut, you can always do it a bit more manual. If you make the subplots yourself, and plot each column separately on a subplot, then you can use a list to indicate the colors for each bar.\n"
